---
title: Smoky Shish Style Tofu Loaded Flatbreads with Houmous, Roasted Garlic Tzatziki and Pickled Onion Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Smoky Shish Style Tofu Loaded Flatbreads are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - smoky base paste! This little pouch of flavour contains ingredients such as smoked paprika and smoked salt to bring a natural smoky, rich and umami flavour to any dish.

